  "detailed_description": "<strong>ZAP Master</strong> is a 2D, abstract art, base defense/bullet hell game where players click to zap incoming enemies. Enemies spawn in and travel down radial lanes, and if one reaches the end of the lane, it's game over! <br><br>The game also allows you to record your scores, so challenge yourself with players from all over the world and see who has the best reflexes!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/679860/extras/f4a00da037f541e9c1c4f686e8addabb.poster.avif?t=1666984565\" width=200 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/679860/extras/f4a00da037f541e9c1c4f686e8addabb.webm?t=1666984565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/679860/extras/f4a00da037f541e9c1c4f686e8addabb.mp4?t=1666984565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
